de>netbox-ceph</code> for NetBox Plugin Certification.</p>"},{"location":"release-notes/version-0.0.1.post1/#changed","title":"Changed","text":"<ul> <li>Added top-level Apache-2.0 license evidence and explicit package metadata.</li> <li>Updated the <code>netbox-proxbox</code> dependency range to <code>&gt;=0.0.18,&lt;0.1.0</code>.</li> <li>Documented compatibility with NetBox <code>v4.5.8</code> and <code>v4.6.1</code>.</li> <li>Added certification evidence docs and support links.</li> <li>Expanded Docker install smoke coverage across NetBox <code>v4.5.8</code> and <code>v4.6.1</code>.</li> </ul>"},{"location":"release-notes/version-0.0.1.post1/#compatibility","title":"Compatibility","text":"NetBox netbox-ceph netbox-proxbox Python v4.5.8 v0.0.1.post1 &gt;=0.0.18,&lt;0.1.0 3.12+ v4.6.1 v0.0.1.post1 &gt;=0.0.18,&lt;0.1.0 3.12+"}]}